---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '~/components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclosures"
  description="Legal disclosures, privacy policy, and accredited-investor information for Adams Summit Partners."
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="Legal" heading="Disclosures &amp; Privacy." />

  <section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-prose prose-brand space-y-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
        Last reviewed: pending counsel review, 2026-04-22.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">General Disclosure</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          The information on this website is provided for informational purposes only and
          does not constitute an offer to sell, or a solicitation of an offer to buy, any
          securities. Any such offer or solicitation will be made only through formal
          offering documents to qualified investors in jurisdictions where permitted by law.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Investment Risks</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          Investments in private real estate involve substantial risk, including the
          potential loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results.
          Projected returns and investment performance are estimates based on current
          assumptions and subject to change. Real estate investments are illiquid and
          investors should be prepared to hold their interests for the full term of the
          investment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Accredited Investors</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          Private investment offerings are made only to accredited investors as defined
          under Rule 501 of Regulation D of the Securities Act of 1933, as amended.
          Investors may be required to verify accredited status prior to investment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Private Investor Area</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          Any materials shared through a password-protected area of this site are provided
          for informational purposes only to people we have established a relationship with,
          and do not constitute an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to buy any
          security. Access to that area does not create an investor relationship. Offerings
          are made only through formal offering documents to accredited investors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Forward-Looking Statements</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          Certain information on this website may constitute forward-looking statements.
          Such statements are subject to known and unknown risks and uncertainties that
          could cause actual results to differ materially from those expressed or implied.
          Adams Summit Partners undertakes no obligation to publicly update any
          forward-looking statements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Jurisdiction</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          Offerings, when made, are limited to jurisdictions where such offerings are
          lawful. Adams Summit Partners is not registered as a broker-dealer, investment
          adviser, or funding portal with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission or
          any state securities authority. Nothing on this website constitutes legal, tax,
          or investment advice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Privacy</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          We collect only the information you provide to us through forms or direct
          communication, and we use it solely to respond to your inquiries and share
          information about investment opportunities. We do not sell or share your
          information with third parties other than service providers necessary to operate
          our business.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy mb-3">Contact for Legal Questions</h2>
        <span class="gold-rule mb-4"></span>
        <p>
          Questions about these disclosures or our privacy practices can be directed to
          <a href="mailto:invest@adamssummitpartners.com" class="underline text-navy hover:text-gold">invest@adamssummitpartners.com</a>.
          Adams Summit Partners is based in Kaysville, Utah.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60 pt-8 border-t border-navy/10">
        This page contains general information only and should be reviewed by legal counsel
        before being relied upon. Adams Summit Partners is not a registered broker-dealer
        or investment adviser.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
